{
  "stem": "294.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On his horse, without his horse, he was the person who was most terribly feared by everybody, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We heard-- you know, when we came, at the time when I was still working in Plaszow, but going to work out-- I mean going to work outside of Plaszow, we used to come when it was already dark, in the winter days.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were being control by the gates, you know, to the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- we had-- we had the lice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had started to have the lice, especially in the summer months, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We also had bed--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "19-- 1943 we came to the camp, right?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was '43, '44 until we left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also, the terrible plague was bed bugs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We slept on the bunks, and in the warm summer months, you know, it was so terribly hot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was like a shower of bed bugs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They used to go in your ears, in your noses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I never forget the day--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bed bugs are when the house is not very clean.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think in America-- [LAUGHS] --they exist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's like-- I think it's a little reddish-- small and reddish in color, brownish-reddish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Horrible.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They bite you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They bite you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they used to come down from-- I don't know-- from the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to have it in our noses and in our ears.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I never forget that that part-- one particular night we couldn't stand it anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we decided-- in front of our barracks was like some ground, grassy ground, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So some of us decided to go and sleep in front of the barrack.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
